recommendations.codeExample:
Review the implementation of the Google Funding Choices (or similar consent management platform) script. Ensure it's loaded efficiently and that redundant calls are minimized. Consider using a single, deferred script load. Example (pseudo-code): 
```javascript
let consentScriptLoaded = false;
function loadConsentScript() {
  if (!consentScriptLoaded) {
    // Load script logic here
    consentScriptLoaded = true;
  }
}
// Call loadConsentScript on initial page load or user interaction if necessary
```
